          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1713264472964-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>mayo </strong>with the <strong>remaining peri peri spice mix </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water </strong>– this is your <strong>peri peri mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1713264477843-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
