            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>peri peri-spiced fish cake </strong>with the <strong>chips</strong>, <strong>spicy peas</strong> and <strong>peri peri mayo </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
